that responsibility.

1569
01:28:53,924 --> 01:28:55,341
There they are.

1570
01:29:03,967 --> 01:29:05,468
Look at that.

1571
01:29:05,502 --> 01:29:08,054
Time to quit smoking.

1572
01:29:08,105 --> 01:29:10,439
It's a good resolution.

1573
01:29:10,474 --> 01:29:12,808
Well...

1574
01:29:12,842 --> 01:29:14,810
