It never has.

1577
01:29:20,701 --> 01:29:23,119
Guys like us,
that's why we get paid.

1578
01:29:23,153 --> 01:29:25,454
- Us?
- Fine.

1579
01:29:25,489 --> 01:29:27,690
You get paid to think about things
they don't want to think about

1580
01:29:27,708 --> 01:29:30,859
